<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Kranthis Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300">
    <script src="js/jquery-2.1.4.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
  	<div class="container">
      <!-- Header with a logo & heading-->
      <header>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-6"><img src="./images/logo.png" class="img-responsive top-logo left-block" alt="portfolio logo" id="imgLogo" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalText"></div>
          <div class="col-md-6 text-right text-uppercase">
              <h1 class="text-thin text-large">Kranthi Kiran</h1>
              <h6>Front-end Developer</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
        	<hr>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content in the middle-->
      <section>
        <div class="row text-center wrapper center-block">
          <div class="col-md-4">
              <img src="./images/carphoto.jpg" class="img-responsive center-block" alt="Personal photo">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8 text-center text-thin text-white">
              <h3>Hello world! I am Kranthi from India working for GE. A decade of IT experience mostly building web applications and worked on all the web tiers. Nice to be part of Udacity to learn this course as front end developer.
              </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer that has featured works & project images-->
      <footer>
        <div class="row">
        	<div class="col-md-12">
            	<h2 class="text-grey">Featured Work</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="./images/personalprojects.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Personal project" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalPersonalProjects">
            <h3>Personal projects</h3>
            <p>
              <a href="#" id="perProjLink" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalPersonalProjects">Link to project</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="./images/Officialwork.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Official work">
            <h3>Official work</h3>
            <p><a href="#">Link to project</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="./images/travel.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Leisure time" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalTravelPage">
            <h3>Leisure time</h3>
            <p><a href="#" id="travelPageLink" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalTravelPage">Link to project</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
    <!-- Leasure travel time modal page -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalTravelPage" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalTravelLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalTravelLabel">Travel page</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <img class="img-responsive" src="images/veggies_small.jpg" alt="Travel & grow my veggies page">
            <p>During my leisure time, I spend in travelling to nature beauty places and grow my veggies in my corridor & terrace.
              I also like reading spiritual books and doing yoga & meditation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Personal projects modal page -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalPersonalProjects" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalPerProjLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalPerProjLabel">Personal projects page</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <img class="img-responsive" src="images/personalprojects_small.jpg" alt="Personal projects page">
            <p>These are my personal projects that I have built in the year 2008. It was my designer who has created photoshop mockup and I have coded all the web tiers. One was a forum application named www.thedrusya.com and the other one was an online shopping cart for herbal products, www.gloherbals.com</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- First Modal Page -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalText" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">My first modal Page</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <img class="img-responsive" src="images/logo.png" alt="Modal logo page">
            <p>This was my first project in this class. I learned a lot about HTML and CSS.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>